  <div class="card">
    <h2>Reflection</h2>
    <p>
      Enhancing SYLTrack strengthened my understanding of how design decisions impact maintainability, scalability, and user experience.
      I learned that building a stable foundation first makes future improvements easier and reduces technical debt. A key challenge was
      balancing new features (like improved dashboards and navigation flow) while maintaining clean structure and readable code.
      Overall, this artifact reflects my growth in software engineering practices and my ability to improve an existing solution using
      professional design principles.
    </p>
